          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="OGkb9ryLzSHwRinIpaYU-4" edge="1" parent="1" source="node_ws_cluster" style="endArrow=classic;html=1;rounded=0;exitX=0.65;exitY=1.061;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;exitPerimeter=0;entryX=0.342;entryY=-0.017;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;entryPerimeter=0;" target="node_redis_2" value="">
          <mxGeometry height="50" relative="1" width="50" as="geometry">
            <mxPoint x="480" y="300" as="sourcePoint" />
            <mxPoint x="530" y="250" as="targetPoint" />
          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="OGkb9ryLzSHwRinIpaYU-8" edge="1" parent="1" source="node_ws_cluster" style="endArrow=classic;html=1;rounded=0;exitX=0.5;exitY=0;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;" value="">
          <mxGeometry height="50" relative="1" width="50" as="geometry">
            <mxPoint x="370" y="190" as="sourcePoint" />
            <mxPoint x="350" y="-20" as="targetPoint" />
          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="OGkb9ryLzSHwRinIpaYU-15" edge="1" parent="1" source="OGkb9ryLzSHwRinIpaYU-12" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;" target="OGkb9ryLzSHwRinIpaYU-14" value="">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="OGkb9ryLzSHwRinIpaYU-21" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h2 data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot;&gt;1. Functional Requirements&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;4,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Decoupled Ingest:&lt;/b&gt; The &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;4,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;22&quot;&gt;WebSocket Cluster&lt;/b&gt; must only handle binary ingestion and producer-side Kafka buffering, separating network I/O from heavy transcoding.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;4,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Reactive Stream Orchestration:&lt;/b&gt; The &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;4,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;35&quot;&gt;Puller Service&lt;/b&gt; must dynamically spawn/kill consumer groups based on CDC events from &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;4,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;119&quot;&gt;Redis Cluster 2&lt;/b&gt; (Stream Meta).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4,2,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;4,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;High Availability (Active/Passive):&lt;/b&gt; Every stream must have a secondary consumer group in a &quot;Passive&quot; state to take over if the &quot;Active&quot; Puller node fails.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4,3,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;4,3,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Stateful Connection Tracking:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;4,3,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;30&quot;&gt;Redis Cluster 1&lt;/b&gt; must maintain a real-time registry of which WS Server holds which User connection to allow for targeted disconnects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4,4,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;4,4,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Automated Cleanup:&lt;/b&gt; Upon session termination (heartbeat loss), the system must kill the &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;4,4,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;87&quot;&gt;ProcessBuilder&lt;/code&gt; and flush local disk buffers to &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;4,4,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;134&quot;&gt;S3&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="410" width="840" x="100" y="930" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="OGkb9ryLzSHwRinIpaYU-25" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h2 data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot;&gt;2. Non-Functional Requirements&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;6&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;6,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Horizontal Scalability:&lt;/b&gt; The system must scale the &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;6,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;50&quot;&gt;Pusher&lt;/b&gt; (Ingest) and &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;6,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;70&quot;&gt;Puller&lt;/b&gt; (Transcode) tiers independently based on CPU/Network metrics.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;6,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Fault Tolerance:&lt;/b&gt; No single point of failure (NSPF) in the message bus or session registry.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6,2,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;6,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Strict Ordering:&lt;/b&gt; Kafka must use &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;6,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;32&quot;&gt;streamID&lt;/code&gt; as the partition key to ensure binary blobs are processed by FFmpeg in the exact order they were sent.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;6,3,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;6,3,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Observability:&lt;/b&gt; Integrated logging of FFmpeg output via &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;6,3,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;55&quot;&gt;Java Virtual Threads&lt;/b&gt; to monitor transcoding health without thread starvation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="230" width="870" x="100" y="1300" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="OGkb9ryLzSHwRinIpaYU-29" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="get signed url" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="200" x="670" y="-210" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
</mxfile>
